{"tid":384163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁游終極敗訴   英御用大狀無奈抨論：「This is Hong Kong」","createTime":"2017-09-02T05:51:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T06:50:03.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1808560284d90ea5d2470a36744845fe86e2f73b","tid":384163,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T05:51:48.000Z","msg":"上星期五，前立法會議員梁頌恆同游蕙禎被DQ嘅終極上訴申請失敗，梁頌恆喺法院出嚟後更加眼紅紅。原來佢哋本身對上訴申請幾有信心，梁搵到英國御用大狀彭力克（David Pannick）代表，彭大狀擅長公法訴訟，亦係人權法專家，律政司亦都曾經多次搵彭大狀幫手打官司。<br />\n<br />\n據聞，今次彭大狀肯幫手，係因為覺得政府DQ民選議員，係一件十分之「nonsense（荒謬）」嘅事，所以主動接觸梁游嘅律師團隊，問有冇需要幫忙。對於最後敗訴，佢都覺得十分無奈，仲講咗句：「This is Hong Kong.」<br />\n<br />\n曾經有媒體話，彭力克每日律師費高達二百萬，肯定梁游背後有外國勢力支持先至俾得起巨額律師費。梁頌恆解釋，之前眾籌嘅一百萬已經足夠俾佢哋兩個嘅律師費同之前嘅庭費，相信彭大狀「收少咗一個零」。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20170901/543802\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20170901%2F543802&d=3E2S4kqCu%2B4ZpRspNF8hZhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=f6861e63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20170901%2F543802&h=b4b8b769\" target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20170901/543802</a>"},{"pid":"db45add1def9f299aaf31b66f094b0d33490e994","tid":384163,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T05:56:21.000Z","msg":"所以我不嬲話, 香港法律界100%由垃圾組成, 係無錯既<br />\n<br />\n一對比下外國普通法大狀 / 律師講既野, 再睇返香港班COSPLAYERS<br />\n分別就好明顯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170902/large/1504328540_6954.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170902%2Flarge%2F1504328540_6954.jpg&h=9be7a094&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c4d6daae5f69d3affe4f1d167406058802b32f6d","tid":384163,"uid":5462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T05:58:47.000Z","msg":"This is China"},{"pid":"1e9909eed0efcd1b05b7cf68dccdfadb9bb94c4b","tid":384163,"uid":25902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T06:06:59.000Z","msg":"香港已死"},{"pid":"c4ef72e3dbc43747cd81e6975f359b07279a8c41","tid":384163,"uid":102096,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T06:25:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c9fa777a28531a629ffe7b904683e0abdc0d4a77","tid":384163,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T06:28:06.000Z","msg":"大狀：理撚得你，記住比返份糧我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff8348edbcaf9d22c544254ddbef02cd66813fee","tid":384163,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T06:28:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>this is 美國都係輸架啦<br />\n都依家仲唔明自己做錯咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n錯在相信香港法律 曬錢去上訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0a30579b7d596eb3c45f3ae37bd6f314fda21e0","tid":384163,"uid":135066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T06:30:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>this is 美國都係輸架啦<br />\n都依家仲唔明自己做錯咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n錯嘅係中共<br />\n唔係佢哋"},{"pid":"d4081c48e425f57fb177dccf5c4fa932f32c9f38","tid":384163,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T06:33:41.000Z","msg":"贏左就my power powerful啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbb30aaa6ec164f09eab742f1bdb7cf45861a8a8","tid":384163,"uid":100010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T06:35:52.000Z","msg":"英國佬既垃圾法律全部唔要， 人治萬歲！"},{"pid":"a1c7028dad768a4e496d23c1bc7b82362a0165b2","tid":384163,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T06:36:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以我不嬲話, 香港法律界100%由垃圾組成, 係無錯既<br />\n<br />\n一對比下外國普通法大狀 / 律師講既野, 再睇返香港班COSPLAYERS<br />\n分別就好明顯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170902/large/1504328540_6954.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170902%2Flarge%2F1504328540_6954.jpg&h=9be7a094&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n無錯，當年咁多香港大律師反對23條，係得Pannick QC擇善固執話23條既立法建議並無不恰當之處，真係令我好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.basiclaw23.gov.hk/chinese/resources/pannick/pannick3.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.basiclaw23.gov.hk%2Fchinese%2Fresources%2Fpannick%2Fpannick3.htm&d=3E2S4kqCu%2B4ZpRspNF8hZhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=85821f3e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.basiclaw23.gov.hk/chinese/resources/pannick/pannick3.htm</a>"},{"pid":"4777bd64c05d1e9708b8bf557052e74385c76c2b","tid":384163,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T06:38:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>this is 美國都係輸架啦<br />\n都依家仲唔明自己做錯咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你幾時死？"},{"pid":"8c6d725de8e73f475e0fa1e03928cbcac3671997","tid":384163,"uid":142358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T06:46:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/02/144643_49d9671c109a0a1721d1f0bd7d9b571c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F02%2F144643_49d9671c109a0a1721d1f0bd7d9b571c.jpg&h=05e81318&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"de123373d861f96b3c9e6b6a549e3f248ce78407","tid":384163,"uid":61210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T06:50:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}